snippet.textDisplay: Y'all have to understand why they are acting this way. They aren't treating this like Dani is dying or they'll never see her again. They've been doing this for ten years as 6 sisters. Just thinking of doing videos without her or tours or meet and greets that's like a big part of Cimorelli that will be missing. For those of us who have watched this group for years have gotten to basically watch Dani grow up. It has to be hard for the older sisters to see her as an adult, married and really pushing towards starting her own life and the things she wants to accomplish because she's not little anymore but they are happy for her. Not to mention these videos were such a bonding time for them so for 99% of them to be without someone who's been in them for 10 years has got to be hard. Christina, Katherine, Lisa, Amy, Lauren and Dani you girls are amazing! Dani I'm so happy you are following your passions girl! Love y'all!
